NEW YORK Thirteen
branches of the NAACP will
observe their 5Oth anniversary
this year. Local branches char
tered so years ago include Alton.
ILL: Buffalo. N. Y: Ell Paso.
Texas,


Texas: Harrisburg. Pa: Los An
geles. Calf: Louisville, KY:
Minneapolis. Mimi: Newark. N.
j.: Pittsburgh, Pa; Shreveport.
La; and Wilmington. Del. Also.
in 1914 an NAACP college chap
ter was organized on the campus
Of Virginia Union University in
Richmond. others include St.
Louis and Portland, Ore.


There are an additional 81
branches and two college chap
tiers that we're chartered more
than half century ago. The,
Chicago branch was organized in
1910. The New York City branch
was started in 1911.


Other early branches include
Baltimore, Boston, Detroit and
the District Of Columbia. 1912;
and the following established In
1913: Indianapolis. Kansas City,
Mo-: Cleveland. Philadelphia.
Seattle, Northern California,
Quincy, ILL.,: Tacoma. WASH:
Muskogee. Okla; Orange, NJ:
Providence. RI; St. Paul. MIMI:
Talladega. Ala: Topeka. Kans.;
and Trenton, NJ.


Also chartered in 1913 were
NAACP chapters at Cornell Uni
versity and Howard University.

Hero Award
full articles.article:
CHICAGO = Howard Spooner,
Negro. city policeman, received
one of the two highest city awards
for heroiSm.


Spooner was cited for wounding
and capturing an armed robber
during a liquor store robbery
La st March. He was off duty
at the time.
